{"tid":1089012,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭俊英群組「金姓歌手」身份曝光！　是「小開」Roy Kim","createTime":"2019-04-02T12:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T14:10:09.000Z","uid":188406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5127031bef353d13ce5598dd0a9ae2617c1390f","tid":1089012,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"記者蕭采薇／綜合報導<br />\n南韓歌手鄭俊英3月遭爆涉嫌偷拍、散播性愛影片，日前遭警方立案逮捕，現已被移送至首爾地檢署。警方曝光的涉嫌犯罪人數顯示，鄭俊英非法群組多達23個。當中一名「K姓」、「金姓」歌手的身份，韓媒2日爆料就是「小開歌手」Roy Kim。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ukzVUwp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FukzVUwp.jpg&h=eb91007f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓媒《Sport鄉京朝鮮》2日獨家報導，在鄭俊英案中，先前一直未公開的「K姓」、「金姓」歌手，正是以唱抒情歌出名的Roy Kim。報導指出，Roy Kim是以「Roy Gim（로이김）」的名字加入鄭俊英的聊天室，而經過警方調查確認無誤，Roy Kim也以證人身份接受調查。<br />\n但對於此事，Roy Kim的經紀人回覆：「沒聽說這件事， 會向在美國求學的本人（指Roy Kim）確認。」Roy Kim本名金相祐，出身自《Super star K》第4季，和同一比賽出身的歌手鄭俊英感情非常好。Roy Kim的父親是南韓第一米酒集團會長，他因此有「小開歌手」的稱號。<br />\n<br />\n據首爾地檢署透露，鄭俊英非法群組多達23個，不論是1對1對話框或者群組，都有涉嫌散播偷拍的性愛片，警方掌握到群組參與的人數共為16人，其中7人被證實有外流非法影片的嫌疑，剩下9人則是只觀看並未轉傳，因此不被列為調查對象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1413940?from=fb_et_korea&amp;fbclid=IwAR0At0td2H-chzbgIGtkC8YTe98UoKZZug1W05koOuv4N4-tGjK5aJciPPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1413940%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_korea%26fbclid%3DIwAR0At0td2H-chzbgIGtkC8YTe98UoKZZug1W05koOuv4N4-tGjK5aJciPPI&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2Bgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=6cf8c06d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1413940?from=fb_et_korea&amp;fbclid=IwAR0At0td2H-chzbgIGtkC8YTe98UoKZZug1W05koOuv4N4-tGjK5aJciPPI</a>"},{"pid":"1919d4b2d9b6412c5fdbec0be5c274287529c2de","tid":1089012,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做龜公賺得多定掛名天團賺得多"},{"pid":"eccaece7319771e574b289cab60dfaab8c72205b","tid":1089012,"uid":188406,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:48:39.000Z","msg":"對唔住強仁OPPa,之前以為姓金的是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快D回歸SJ啦, 特特同大家等緊你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SM5mP5y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSM5mP5y.gif&h=e4c03946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ew4KNSe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEw4KNSe.gif&h=8f10a17f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b6b070029fb42bd5e52180e2b3463536ac58118","tid":1089012,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"Roy Kim的父親是南韓第一米酒集團會長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185a4caa7bb30738d60686909e709f5235e98c91","tid":1089012,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b6b070029fb42bd5e52180e2b3463536ac58118","tid":1089012,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"Roy Kim的父親是南韓第一米酒集團會長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"大L哂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dec3c39bf388793989a71ed536694fd851cad88","tid":1089012,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T14:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLMETcM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLMETcM.png&h=260801e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n又有強仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/